{
  "stem": "11175.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then they took-- they didn't put this into the trains, the cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They put us in work, that we should go in the Ostbahn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were working in Ostbahn, loading coals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You know, and over there was barracks, very nice barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Some army was there before, and they left the barracks, and we-- you know, we were there-- went there, about a few hundred people, 300, 400 people went in there to that [? hausbarn. ?] And I was between them with these people.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we went-- every day to work, where-- to the railroad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "A lot of coals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We would dig it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We had work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We did a lot of work there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were there in that Ostbahn-- I was there about four or five-- five-- more-- more than five months.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then came the liquidation from the-- from the Ostbahn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is-- this was a different place completely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the transports which they went to Treblinka, and to Majdanek, or somewhere, that was another-- another rail yard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was another-- another place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, we had-- our duty was to load and unload coals and digging and making rails and all kind of hard work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were there, in that-- in that-- Ostbahn, I was there, let's say, from '43 from the-- the uprising from the ghetto until [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [? also ?] September-- before September.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one morning, we were still asleep, it was-- I think it was a Sunday morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- because we were sleeping that time a little longer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We looked out [? and see-- ?] what is Ukrainian doing here?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What is so many SS doing here?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A half an hour later, an order.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Take whatever you have and come out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
